snippet.title: Test Subject Blue Speedrun in 11:11 (WR)
snippet.description:
very good run! still can be improved. 
teleporter glitches can be done faster, levels 14 and 15 have faster strats and i can save an extra second or 2 in other levels such as 23,25,8,13 etc. 
overall my most clean run the only huge choke was on level 21 lol
